                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-card-heading
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold eCommerce
                                p.mb-0 We help eCommerce customers with product recommendation, generate more revenue

